      {
        "nameNarration": "阿莉娜",
        "narration": "我很clear地记得@宠物狗死去时的记忆",
        "narrationEffect": "in",
        "turnChangeOut": "fadeOut",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-1"
      },
      {
        "narration": "就像candle的火焰会在最后变得更加强烈一样@躺在柔软的blanket上的狗就像发抖一样@稍微痉挛了一阵，然后再也不动了",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-2"
      },
      {
        "narration": "直到不久前都像sister一样互相抚摸的pet@一旦失去soul@就变成了肉的block",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-3"
      },
      {
        "narration": "在面前的虽然是lovely的sister@但在阿莉娜看来@它只是个徒有空壳的fake",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-4"
      },
      {
        "narration": "在8岁那一年@阿莉娜开始对live和dead产生了兴趣",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-5"
      },
      {
        "autoTurnLast": 0.5,
        "bg": "bg_adv_21491.jpg",
        "narrationEffect": "out",
        "turnChangeIn": "fadeIn"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "阿莉娜",
        "narration": "自那之后，阿莉娜就不断创作着art@也坚持学习着philosophy@大人们却给我的art加上rating@自顾自地沉醉在了其中",
        "narrationEffect": "in",
        "turnChangeOut": "fadeOut",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-6"
      },
      {
        "narration": "正是因为有过那种经历@成为魔法少女之后，阿莉娜第一次见到魔女的时候@就感受到了一种令人无比兴奋的pressure",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-7"
      },
      {
        "narration": "魔女那又psychedelic又emotional@还无比sensational的姿态@就像自顾自地沉醉的大人们一样@如同一面映照着即便死去@也要被欲望支配的人类的明镜一样",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-8"
      },
      {
        "narration": "自从知道人类不仅因为war@还会沉溺于自己的欲求而毁灭之后@魔女在阿莉娜眼中就变得愈加lovely了",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-9"
      },
      {
        "autoTurnLast": 0.5,
        "bg": "black",
        "narrationEffect": "out",
        "turnChangeIn": "fadeIn"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "阿莉娜",
        "narration": "人终会毁灭@明明抗拒地哭个不停@在心底，他们却是带着笑容死去的",
        "narrationEffect": "in",
        "turnChangeOut": "fadeOut",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-10"
      },
      {
        "narration": "所以，阿莉娜虽然想给予人类毁灭@但只要看到大家resist的姿态@阿莉娜就会感到无比兴奋、不能自已",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103303/vo_full_103303-7-11"
      },
